name: Megurine Luka Theme - Roblox
description:
Check out the original style at userstyles.org
This is a follow-up to a request, so the theme colo(u)rs might not be most well suited, do give feedback on how to make it better. All credits go to >Project Sekai: Colorful Stage< since they're the game this background is from. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
